{"word":"διαφερόντως","slug":"διαφερόντως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαφερόντως</b></el>  (diafero/ntws) adverb<p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> of <a href='S:διαφέρω'><el>διαφέρω</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>differently from, at odds with</i>, <el>διαφερόντως ἤ . .</el> , <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>διαφερόντως τῶν ἄλλων</el> <i>above</i> all others, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>eminently, especially</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}